<div class="hero rounded-4 p-4 p-lg-5 mb-4 position-relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="row align-items-center g-4">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <p class="eyebrow text-uppercase mb-2">Idle skate sim</p>
      <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">Stick Skater</h1>
      <p class="lead mb-4">Stack tricks, rack XP, and let your stick figure hustle for coins while you chill. Build the ultimate flow, gear up, and rule the leaderboard.</p>
      <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
        <a class="btn btn-skate" href="<%= play_path %>">Start a run</a>
        <a class="btn btn-outline-light" href="<%= leaderboard_path %>">View leaderboard</a>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-4 text-light">
        <span class="badge bg-skate-soft text-dark">Idle gains</span>
        <span class="badge bg-skate-soft text-dark">Gear boosts</span>
        <span class="badge bg-skate-soft text-dark">Style points</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6 text-lg-end">
      <div class="glass-card p-4">
        <p class="text-uppercase fw-semibold small text-muted mb-2">Current run</p>
        <div class="row g-3">
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="stat-tile">
              <span class="stat-label">XP</span>
              <span class="stat-value">12,450</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="stat-tile">
              <span class="stat-label">Coins</span>
              <span class="stat-value">3,210</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="stat-tile">
              <span class="stat-label">Best trick</span>
              <span class="stat-value">360 Flip</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="stat-tile">
              <span class="stat-label">Run time</span>
              <span class="stat-value">02:18:44</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="btn btn-outline-dark w-100 mt-3" href="<%= shop_path %>">Upgrade loadout</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-shape"></div>
</div>

<div class="row g-3 g-lg-4 mb-4">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card h-100 card-shadow border-0">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-2">Flow without grinding</h5>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Your skater keeps earning while you’re away. Come back to bigger stacks and trick chains ready to cash in.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card h-100 card-shadow border-0">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-2">Gear that matters</h5>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Boards, wheels, and bearings all boost speed, style, or coin multipliers. Tune your loadout for the meta.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="card h-100 card-shadow border-0">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-2">Climb the leaderboard</h5>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Compete on runs, combos, and passive income. Every session pushes you closer to legend status.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="rounded-4 p-4 p-lg-5 bg-white card-shadow">
  <div class="row g-4 align-items-center">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Build a skate empire</h3>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">From a chipped deck to pro-level hardware, every upgrade compounds your idle gains. Queue runs, cash out, reinvest, repeat.</p>
      <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <div class="pill">
          <span class="pill-dot bg-success"></span>
          <span>Passive income per hour</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pill">
          <span class="pill-dot bg-warning"></span>
          <span>Style multiplier</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pill">
          <span class="pill-dot bg-info"></span>
          <span>Combo streak bonus</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div class="progress-stack">
        <div class="progress-label d-flex justify-content-between mb-1">
          <span>Coins per minute</span>
          <span>+42%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="progress bg-light" role="progressbar" aria-label="Coins" aria-valuenow="42" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
          <div class="progress-bar bg-skate" style="width: 42%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-label d-flex justify-content-between mt-3 mb-1">
          <span>Speed boost</span>
          <span>+65%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="progress bg-light" role="progressbar" aria-label="Speed" aria-valuenow="65" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
          <div class="progress-bar bg-dark" style="width: 65%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-label d-flex justify-content-between mt-3 mb-1">
          <span>Style factor</span>
          <span>+78%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="progress bg-light" role="progressbar" aria-label="Style" aria-valuenow="78" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
          <div class="progress-bar bg-warning" style="width: 78%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
